      "notes": "NEC MultiSync 4FG (JC-1531VMA, 1990). Service manual on archive.org confirms 0.28 mm black-matrix shadow mask, 15\" FST tube / 14\" viewable, native 1024×768 at 4:3 (the 5:4 era starts with the later 5FG-onward FE/FP). H 27–57 kHz auto-sync, V 55–90 Hz. Picked 50 kHz / 75 Hz as a typical mid-range operating point (1024×768@75 Hz)."
    }
